comments: Julianne is really helpful and inspires ideas. She is talented, hardworking and friendly.

Grad Student. Great teacher. I was not into printmaking, but had to take it for art major. Projects can all be finished within class time, unless u are absent a lot. Monoprint, DryPt, Lito, etc. 2 projects for each style (1 choice & 2 teacher\'s) A good intro class for those who don\'t understand printmaking!!!
Grad student. Very friendly and helpful. Great, great class, no complaints.
